node.title: Auckland police find vehicles used in overnight ram raid but burglars yet to be found
node.description: Auckland police are investigating an overnight ram raid.
node.content:
["", "
Police attended a ram raid at an Auckland store last night. Photo: 123RF
", "Auckland police are investigating an overnight ram raid.", "Police were called around 1am on Saturday to a commercial business after a vehicle was used to gain entry.", "Burglars entered the store and stole items before fleeing in another vehicle.", "Police found the second vehicle abandoned a short time later but the burglars are yet to be located."]
